msgid ""
"Loop a calming sound during focus. White/pink/brown noise and rain/sea are "
"built in; pick \"Custom file\" to use your own."
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->focus_ambient_sound->description
msgid "Play an ambient sound during focus"
msgstr "專注期間播放背景音"

#. settings-schema.json->focus_ambient_sound->tooltip
msgid ""
"Loop a soft ambient sound during focus — the built-in brown noise, or your "
"own file below."
msgstr "專注期間循環播放柔和的背景音——內建的棕噪音，或下面你自己的檔案。"

#. settings-schema.json->focus_ambient_volume->description
msgid "Ambient volume"
msgstr "背景音量"

#. settings-schema.json->focus_ambient_volume->tooltip
msgid "Volume of the ambient sound (0 = silent)."
msgstr "背景音的音量（0 = 靜音）。"

#. settings-schema.json->focus_ambient_preview_button->description
msgid "▶ Preview"
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->focus_ambient_preview_button->tooltip
msgid "Play a short sample of the chosen ambient sound at the set volume."
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->break_breathing->description
msgid "Show a breathing guide during breaks"
msgstr "休息時顯示呼吸引導"

#. settings-schema.json->break_breathing->tooltip
msgid ""
"During breaks, show an expanding and contracting circle that paces your "
"breathing to help you unwind."
msgstr "休息時顯示一個放大與縮小的圓圈，為你的呼吸定速，幫助你放鬆。"

#. settings-schema.json->break_lock_enabled->description
msgid "Lock the screen during breaks"
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->break_lock_enabled->tooltip
msgid ""
"When a break starts, show a brief warning and then lock the screen so you "
"actually step away. Never locks during focus; off by default."
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->break_lock_long_only->description
msgid "Lock only on long breaks"
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->break_lock_long_only->tooltip
msgid "Only lock for the longer breaks, not every short break."
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->zen_mode_enabled->description
msgid ""
"Enable Zen mode (focus spotlight — dims other windows, toggled from the menu)"
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->zen_mode_enabled->tooltip
msgid ""
"Allow the focus spotlight, toggled from the menu: while focusing, the other "
"windows dim so the one you're working in stands out."
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->zen_dim_strength->units
msgid "%"
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->zen_dim_strength->description
msgid "Zen spotlight: dim strength"
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->zen_dim_strength->tooltip
msgid ""
"How much to darken the other windows while a focus session runs (higher = "
"darker)."
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->zen_dim_desktop->description
msgid "Zen spotlight: also dim the desktop wallpaper"
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->zen_dim_desktop->tooltip
msgid "Darken the desktop background too, not just the other windows."
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->strict_focus->description
msgid "Strict focus: no pause or skip during a focus block"
msgstr "嚴格專注：專注區塊期間不可暫停或跳過"

#. settings-schema.json->strict_focus->tooltip
msgid ""
"While a focus block is running, hide pause and skip so you commit to it. You "
"can still Reset to abandon the session — it's never a hard lock."
msgstr ""
"專注區塊進行時隱藏暫停與跳過，讓你專心投入。你仍可重設以放棄此工作階段 — 絕非"
"強制鎖定。"

#. settings-schema.json->focus_dnd->description
msgid "Mute notifications while focusing (Do Not Disturb)"
msgstr "專注時靜音通知（勿擾）"

#. settings-schema.json->focus_dnd->tooltip
msgid "Mute Cinnamon notifications while focusing; restored afterwards."
msgstr "專注時靜音 Cinnamon 通知；之後會恢復。"

#. settings-schema.json->pause_media->description
msgid "Pause music & video on breaks and pauses"
msgstr "休息和暫停時暫停音樂與影片"

#. settings-schema.json->pause_media->tooltip
msgid ""
"Pauses any playing media (browser tab, music app via MPRIS) when a break or "
"pause starts, and resumes the same players when focus continues."
msgstr ""
"當休息或暫停開始時，暫停所有正在播放的媒體（瀏覽器分頁、透過 MPRIS 的音樂應用"
"程式），並在專注繼續時恢復相同的播放器。"

#. settings-schema.json->run_command_enabled->description
msgid "Run a command when focus or a break starts"
msgstr "專注或休息開始時執行指令"

#. settings-schema.json->run_command_enabled->tooltip
msgid "Run a command of your choice when focus or a break starts."
msgstr "在專注或休息開始時執行你指定的指令。"

#. settings-schema.json->focus_start_command->description
msgid "Command to run when focus starts"
msgstr "專注開始時執行的指令"

#. settings-schema.json->focus_start_command->tooltip
msgid ""
"Pick a script to run when a focus block starts (e.g. enable Do Not Disturb). "
"You can also type a command."
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->break_start_command->description
msgid "Command to run when a break starts"
msgstr "休息開始時執行的指令"

#. settings-schema.json->break_start_command->tooltip
msgid ""
"Pick a script to run when a break starts (e.g. clear your status). You can "
"also type a command."
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->goal_command->description
msgid "Command to run when the daily goal is reached"
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->goal_command->tooltip
msgid ""
"Pick a script to run when you reach your daily goal (e.g. a small "
"celebration). You can also type a command."
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->pushover_enabled->description
msgid "Send push notifications to your phone (Pushover)"
msgstr "傳送推播通知到你的手機（Pushover）"

#. settings-schema.json->pushover_enabled->tooltip
msgid ""
"Send a push notification to your devices via Pushover when focus or breaks "
"start."
msgstr "在專注或休息開始時，透過 Pushover 傳送推播通知到你的裝置。"

#. settings-schema.json->pushover_help->description
msgid ""
"Free phone/desktop alerts. Sign up at pushover.net and paste your keys below."
msgstr "免費的手機/桌面提醒。在 pushover.net 註冊，然後在下方貼上你的金鑰。"

